    What is Postman used?
    What is Postman Used for? Postman is a software application that allows developers to test, document, and share APIs (Application Programming Interfaces). Developers widely use it to simplify the process of testing APIs by providing a user-friendly interface for making requests, viewing responses, and debugging issues.29 Nov 2024

    Is Postman an Indian company?
    This article relies excessively on references to primary sources. Please improve this article by adding secondary or tertiary sources. Postman is an Indian-origin global software company that offers an API platform for developers to design, build, test, and collaborate on APIs.
